cast.overview: An endearing modern-day story about how the lovable Goof bonds with his teenage son Max on a hilarious cross-country road trip. En route to the ol' fishing hole, they find themselves up to their floppy ears in misadventure!
cast.title: A Goofy Movie

details.biography:
Brittany Smith (born September 21, 1985), also formerly known by her stage name Matisse, is an American singer, songwriter, actress, and model. She was one half of the pop duo Brit & Alex with her identical twin sister, until their split in 2009.

She was also an actress when she was young, such as in the film Goofy or Pinocchio: Revenge.
details.name: Brittany Alyse Smith
